E1B4AUD.original: ~z~I thought it was a Pole or a Serb or something?
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~我记得是波兰人还是塞尔维亚人吧？

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~That brown ain't gonna leave here with you Losers.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~海洛因是不可能被你们失败者抢走的。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~You best look to the right, my brother. More of our friends are coming.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~最好注意下右边，好兄弟。又来了不少朋友。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Tell you what, send me a fucking link to that Ashley video. What do I care what she's up to? We're through.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~这样吧，你把Ashley那部片的链接发我。我管她那么多干嘛？我们结束了。
~z~你们这些失败者是来抢我们的海洛因的？

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~The two of them are not always mutually exclusive, my brother.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~这两者可以是不矛盾的，好兄弟。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~That's why we do what we do,
~z~Why, how - they're the same fucking thing.
~z~Look. We got a whole van load of Deadbeats to deal with.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~看，我们有一整车的死妈天使要打。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Where'd the hell I get it? What is wrong with you?
~z~Crack that can open, boys. The Deadbeat van has arrived.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~开盖有奖，小的们。死妈天使的外卖来了。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Lost MC are a bunch of liberal pussies.
~z~Oh, shit, you sonofabitch. I was hoping you'd go OTB or somethin'. Good driving.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~噢操，妈了个逼的。我还以为你会放水的。好车技。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~No one sets fire to AOD property and lives to tell it.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~放火烧死亡天使的地盘就别想跑了。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~We said adios to another brother today, Johnny.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~今天才刚跟另一个兄弟道过别，Johnny。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~What the fuck are you talking about?

E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~知不知道摩托车的工作原理？

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~You gonna take out that Deadbeat on the stairs or do I gotta do everything?
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~赶紧把楼梯上的死妈天使干掉，别让我包办好吧。
~z~你们有我们想要的东西，死妈天使。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~That's got to be the last nail in our chapter's casket, don't it?
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~这就是压死我们分会的最后一根稻草了吧？

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Do me a favor- help keep this degenerate out of jail, alright,
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~帮我个忙，先别让这烂人进去，好吧？

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~We ain't Deadbeats, but you're all fucking dead.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~我们不是死妈天使，但你们死定了。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Have I got a toy for you.
~z~Wake these Deadbeats up with a bang, brother.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~一炮打醒这帮死妈天使，兄弟。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Come on, we got another room to handle!
~z~And on their mighty metal steeds they come.
~z~The faster we go, the harder we hit it,
~z~Watch your backs. The AOD are on their bikes.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~都当心点，死亡天使骑着车来了。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Hey asshole, you'd be a lot less ugly with a bullet hole in your face.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~嘿，混蛋，给你脸上开个洞就当是美容了。
~z~你们就要变成菊花炸裂的尸体了。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Hey, Johnny. A.O.D. coming from the right.
~z~Don't you ever get tired of following Billy without knowing what's going on?
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~整天不清楚情况地跟在Billy后面，你不累吗？

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Billy, man. Just for once I'd like to know what the fuck we're doing before we do it.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~Billy，兄弟。我想先知道这次到底要干什么，就这一次。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Brother, you ready for the next room? Go!
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~兄弟，准备好打下一个房间了吗？上！

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, I sure am, Bill. Thanks for pointin' out the glaringly obvious one more time. Later, man.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~对，我傻逼，Bill。谢谢你把显而易见的东西又指出了一次。回见，伙计。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Maybe. Maybe. At least you got Jackie and the kid.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~也许吧，也许吧。至少你还有Jackie跟孩子。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~The AOD reserves are most bounteous, aren't they?
~z~All kind of shit is out there,
~z~Check the Deadbeats down that alleyway, Johnny.
~z~No disrespect in beating you, Bill. I'm still your humble servant.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~比赢了不是不尊重你，Bill。我还是你卑微的仆人。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~We need to clear this whole clubhouse. Go!
~z~Brian, you got yourself killed you fucking moron.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~Brian，你把自己给玩死了，傻逼东西。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Johnny the Jew - how the hell are you?
~z~It sure is war, isn't it, Losers?
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~这就是开战了吧，对吧，失败者？

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Shit, there's an army of Deadbeats coming forth, boys.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，死妈天使的军队来了，小的们。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Don't know about you, but I'm gonna smoke some haze and get me a woman. Take my mind off shit.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~不是很懂你，但我要吞云吐雾找女人去了。好好放松一下。
~z~酒吧打烊了，混蛋们。干掉他们，阿强。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Think nothing of it, brother. We have all got to pull together in this climate of war and uncertainty.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~没关系，兄弟。在不稳定的战争环境下，我们必须要团结一心。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~I hope your fucking legs come off.

E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~骑着摩托的死妈天使还是死妈天使。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~You're outta line, John boy. Stick behind me.
~z~I ain't never been in an AOD clubhouse.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~我还是头一次来死亡天使的会所。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~A biker without a bike. You're one sorry S.O.B., John boy.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~没摩托的骑手。你就是个小傻逼，阿强。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Well, that's something your leader will have to worry about.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~是吗，这种事是你老大我需要操心的。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~What the fuck is wrong with you man?
~z~Now we're gonna steal their smack? Slow down.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~现在还要偷他们的海洛因？慢点。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Sorry to intrude, gentlemen. But we got a little business matter.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~不好意思打扰了，各位。但我们有正事要谈。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~It's not luck, Brian. The man wants you he's gonna come find you no matter how smart you think you are.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~跟运气无关，Brian。存心抓你的话再聪明也没用。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Good race, man. You fuckin' dropped it.
~z~The brothers are doing what you tell 'em to. Maybe that's the problem, Bill. Adios.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~弟兄们都是听你命令行事的。可能这就是问题吧，Bill。再见。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Now take one of these grenades and put it through their window.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~现在，拿上这把榴弹枪，对着窗户来一发。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Almost like a joke, y'know, only it wasn't funny.
~z~I don't need to now that I'm carrying your heavy ass around with me, Johnny.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~没那个必要，带着你这头肥猪跑就够累了，Johnny。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~I'd be nothing but embarrassed to have you kissing my ass all day, Brian.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~你跟在我后面溜须拍马只会让我难堪，Brian。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Stay in formation, Johnny. Get behind me.
~z~The Deadbeats have got themselves one shit-load of heroin.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~死妈天使手头的海洛因还真不少啊。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Yeah I can, Johnny. I can. So fuck you, man. Yeah, fuck you!
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~当然值得，Johnny。值得的。去你妈的，伙计。对，去你妈的！

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~I'm front door on this run, boys.
~z~I seen a video of Ashley fucking on the internet. You're a chump, Johnny.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~我在网上看到了Ashley上镜的黄片。你就一傻逼，Johnny。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~You forgotten your place, soldier? Stay behind the ride captain.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~忘记自己的位置了，士兵？待在行车长后面。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~You gotta stop reading them shitty internet sites, man,
~z~We got more Deadbeats coming at us.
~z~Let's get in there, men. Come on.
~z~The Lost MC is gonna pay for this.
~z~There's a lesson to be learned here. Resources aren't limitless, Johnny.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~有一件事你要明白。资源不是无限的，Johnny。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~How 'bout we drop the hammer on this run, Billy. Make shit interesting.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~这次认真比比怎样，Billy？找点乐子。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~and start thinking about what you're doing to us.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~好好想想你会造成的后果吧。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~That's what you do with a leader, dumbass. Are you sad no one's following you, Johnny?
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~跟在大哥后头就是这样，白痴。没人跟着你你难受吗，Johnny？

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Billy, all you gotta do is grab it.
~z~Well, this is the mother of all fuckups.
~z~I thought you only watched gay porn on the internet, Brian. You're into cock, right?
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~你不是只看基片的吗，Brian。你就喜欢鸡巴，对吧？

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Everything is fucking up around me, man. My bike... my brothers too.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~我身边的一切都被毁了。我的车...还有我的弟兄。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Looks like we ran into an AOD convention. What fun.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~我们好像打扰到死亡天使的大会了，真高兴。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Wow! See, I like how you did that - it was very good, very clever.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~哇哦！你可真会说话，很厉害，很聪明。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Dig some graves, boys. We're about to have some bodies on our hands.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~把坑挖好，小的们。待会儿有尸体要处理。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Billy's bought it, oh shit. Oh shit. What're we going to do! We're fucked!
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~Billy死了，我操。噢，妈的。这我们怎么办！我们完了！

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Time to clear that next room, brother!
~z~You ever heard of Jason Michaels? He was a brother of mine.
~z~Angels of Death MC gonna fuck you, boys.
~z~Our chapter was all I had, Jim. I'll see you round.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~我只有我们的分会，Jim。我们之后见。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Maybe you should start thinking about what that means to you.
~z~Billy, man - please don't be a dick.
~z~Shit, man. Today weren't a good day for our chapter.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，伙计。今天是我们分会的大凶之日啊。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Looks like you got 'em angry, John boy.
~z~No, it wasn't. But what doesn't kill us only...
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~不，不是大凶。但杀不死我们的只会...

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Oh, y'know, from a little contact I have
~z~The Almighty forgives, Johnny. The Lost don't.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~原谅是上帝的事情，Johnny。失落帮绝不姑息。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~You shouldn't a killed our brother, Deadbeats.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~我们的弟兄不是你们能碰的，死妈天使。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~We go faster, longer an' harder and that's how we stay together.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~我们更快更久更强，这样才齐聚一堂。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~We're going into the viper's nest, brothers. Come on.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~这下要进蛇窝了，弟兄们。走吧。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Sure, yeah. I'm sorry for not having enough explosives to fuel your war efforts, Billy. See you.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~是这样没错。对不起，这些榴弹不足以帮你赢得战争，Billy。再见。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~How about we inject some speed into proceedings, Mr. President. See if you still got it?
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~要么我们全速前进吧，会长大人。看看你还行不行？

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Two million in arm candy's as good a payback as I can think of.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~唾手可得的两百万可是最好的弥补。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~you're acting like you don't even give a shit.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~居然是一副漠不关心的样子。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~who really wants you to cut me out of the loop...
~z~that's how we do what we do.
~z~Calm down, Brian. The brothers can pull through this. Now get the fuck out of my face.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~冷静，Brian。弟兄们能够度过难关的。别在我面前碍事了。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~These Deadbeats ain't getting outta this hole, brother.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~这些死妈天使一个都别想逃，兄弟。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~You Losers trying to burn our house?
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~你们失败者想烧我们的会所？

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~These Deadbeats are the ones who killed Jason in Broker.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~在Broker杀害Jason的就是这帮死妈天使。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~I thought this was payback for Jason, man, what the fuck is this?
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~我们不是来替Jason报仇的吗，伙计？这他妈是什么？

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~You want me to give you a thousand words on brotherhood for tomorrow, you asshole?
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~你想让我明天交一份一千字的兄弟情作文吗，混蛋？

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Get the Deadbeats in the bar, Johnny.
~z~Nothing gonna help me forget this shit. See you around, Clay.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~我就没法子这样放松了。之后见，Clay。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Shit. It's like we woke up a whole nest of assholes.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，我们这是捅了死妈窝啊。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Johnny - you seem a little tense lately - have you ever considered some analysis?
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~Johnny，你最近有点紧张啊，有考虑过看医生吗？

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Only people who do time are the ones that are dumb enough to get caught. Apart from Bill. He got unlucky.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~蹲号子的都是蠢到被抓的白痴。除了Bill，他是运气差。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Let's get the fuck outta here. Every man for himself.
~z~Shit, yeah, of course. Only the chapter president gets to know what's going on.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，也是。只有分会会长才能知道具体情况。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Ha ha ha. If you believe that you're a fucking chump. See you round.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~哈哈哈。信那玩意你就是傻逼。之后见。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~These guys are wasted man, take 'em out.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~这些都是人中败类，干掉他们。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~I'm thinking you ride a cage next run. Cos it don't look like you can be trusted to ride a bike.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~下次只能把你关笼子里了。因为不值得把机车托付给你。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~We lift this shit right now and every Deadbeat on the east coast
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~现在拿走这两袋垃圾，东海岸的所有死妈天使

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~Man, these Deadbeats just keep on comin', don't they.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~兄弟，这死妈天使咋杀不完啊，不是吗。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~So where did you get them from?
~z~Brian, man. What you been doing lately. Sucking Billy's cock, I'm betting.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~Brian，伙计。最近你在干嘛，肯定是在舔Billy的屌吧。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~So is this about kicking ass and feeling like big men or are we gonna make some money?
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~这次是要爽一爽装个逼，还是大家一起赚钱？

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~I think you got me confused with Brian. He's the one who's permanently suckered onto your ass.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~你把我跟Brian搞错了吧。他才是你的跟屁虫。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~We got some bad information, brother. These are the guys.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~之前的消息有误，兄弟。他们才是真凶。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~So long, brothers. Wash the taste of gun powder out your mouths with a cold American beer.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~再见，弟兄们。用冰冷的美国啤酒漱掉嘴里的火药吧。

E1B4AUD.original: ~z~They killed that kid and look at you,
~z~-Come on brother. ~n~-Jesus, hold your fucking horses, man.
E1B4AUD.translated: ~z~－走了，兄弟。~n~－天哪，你他妈慢点，伙计。
